{"tid":2290558,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股神執倉！畢菲特沽三百億蘋果股份 掃入四大藥廠","createTime":"2020-11-18T05:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T14:30:48.000Z","uid":259777,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3ab4fe06507f4799cf15e9bc8fc47605fa93474b","tid":2290558,"uid":259777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:47:35.000Z","msg":"股神畢菲特旗下巴郡開始投資四大藥股，押注製藥行業可能會因世界努力走出疫情而受惠。<br />\n<br />\n監管文件顯示，截至9月30日，巴郡在艾伯維（AbbVie）、百時美施貴寶（Bristol-Myers Squibb）、美國默克（Merck）分別新增逾18億美元持股，在輝瑞新增1.36億美元股份，該4隻股份於盤後交易上漲1%至2.8%不等。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，巴郡於第三季減持3,600萬股蘋果，相當於3.7%的蘋果持倉，按蘋果前收市價120.3美元計算，減持的蘋果股份市值達43.3億美元（折合335.6億港元）。巴郡於9月底持有蘋果股份價值1,117億美元。"},{"pid":"5054a9e9ef9ab10bf3b6a773c8ede78fe2e29a17","tid":2290558,"uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:48:34.000Z","msg":"過氣啦廢老"},{"pid":"44b5a026a0a4a0a9bf2b963ba78153fe669d305c","tid":2290558,"uid":987,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:49:32.000Z","msg":"識玩牛熊未"},{"pid":"86328607f01037481e361b555369609e81de1248","tid":2290558,"uid":68220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:49:37.000Z","msg":"幾十億就唔算新聞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0b665e17b6f219801af60d9025f31639166954","tid":2290558,"uid":120908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:59:00.000Z","msg":"連登大戶一晚都唔止啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212d054fbf2727e6bfd27362934c891fe879ccc0","tid":2290558,"uid":239912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:02:09.000Z","msg":"藥股上年尾都炒完啦 而家先入場"},{"pid":"725a80b65e658efed73877928eb27aabf6c7e613","tid":2290558,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:02:50.000Z","msg":"咁遲先入藥廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd9cb185b01df1cfe50820823682c3f61e617d2","tid":2290558,"uid":353804,"